div.p: Lettered at the centre of the plate: 'IN TIMORE AC CHARITATE DEI / DA NIEL MIGNOT FECIT HOC / AVGVSTAE VINDELICORVM' Dated '1593' in the centre of the plate. Signed 'DM' in the lower left and 'F' in the lower right of the plate.
